 <!-- Tabs -->
   <div class="row">
        <div class="container">
            <h3>Tabs</h3>
            <p>Turn the nav menu into navigation tabs with the <code>.nav-tabs</code> class.
                 Add the <code>.active</code> class to the active/current link. 
                 If you want the tabs to be togglable, see the last example on this page.</p>
            <ul class="nav nav-tabs"> 
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="#">Link 1</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Link 2</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Link 3</a></li>
            </ul>
